#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><ul><li>
#: en/genkernel.xml:293
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    <b>--kernel-cc=<c>someCompiler</c></b>: Specifies the compiler employed\n"
"    during the kernel compilation process.\n"
"  "
msgstr ""
"    <b>--kernel-cc=<c>someCompiler</c></b>: これはあなたのカーネルの構築に使われるコンパイラを指定します。\n"
