"  "

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><ul><li>
#: en/genkernel.xml:301
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    <b>--kernel-as=<c>someAssembler</c></b>: Specifies the assembler employed\n"
"    during the kernel compilation process.\n"
"  "
